        "description": "A cracked or shattered bone, graded by how far the break has gone. Severity tracks the worst fracture on the body: a hairline crack nags, but a fully shattered bone (bone HP driven to 0) is agony that collapses strength and dexterity and crawls all work. The struck limb's own function, manipulation for an arm, movement for a leg, is gutted on top via the body model. The limb is NOT lost: bone mends over WEEKS of rest (dressing + a caretaker speed it).",
