        "description": "Severe pain has driven the body into shock, HALF the old unified crisis, the pain half. Strength, dexterity, focus and footing all falter. When it stacks with Hypovolemia (blood-loss shock) the two together are the full crisis of old. Numbed by painkillers/drink.",
        "lethalSeverity": 1.0,
        "floater": true,
        "stages": [
            { "label": "mild",     "minSeverity": 0.0,  "color": "#E0A050", "modifiers": {"strength": 0.9,  "dexterity": 0.9,  "perception": 0.925, "workEfficiency": 0.9,  "moveSpeed": 0.925} },
