    // ── Magical buffs ("magical": true) — PRODUCTION-CHAIN-II §M ──────────────
    // Passive buffs granted by worn attuned gear (and, later, by MAGIC-SKILLS spells/skill nodes
    // through the SAME pipeline). Pushed into transientConditions by syncTransientConditions while the
    // granting item is equipped; they auto-clear on unequip. Now that conditions carry base-stat keys,
    // each gem boosts its thematic ATTRIBUTE (so the bonus flows through combat + every formula), with
    // a smaller work/move bonus on top. The "magical" flag is for UI/lore and a future dispel hook.
